query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('architecture',
'dll',
'google-apps-script',
'list',
'pip',
'printing',
'rabbitmq',
'tuples',
'view',
'visual-studio',
'webdriver',
'xml-parsing');
